The "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" course at 4Geeks Academy is a 16-week program that prepares students for a career in data science. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries, work with supervised and unsupervised learning models, and solve real-life data challenges. The course also focuses on developing AI projects, including the full lifecycle from development to deployment and maintenance. The classes are conducted in small groups with a maximum of 12 students. No previous experience is required. For more information, visit the [website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). Stop.